description:
    War Tank Machine  is an action-packed game that puts players in the driver's seat of a powerful military tank, ready to take on enemy forces on the battlefield. With stunning graphics and immersive gameplay, players will experience the adrenaline rush of warfare as they engage in explosive tank battles across different terrains and landscapes.
As players progress through the game, they can upgrade and customise their tanks with various weapons, armour, and other enhancements to increase their firepower and survivability. They can also team up with other players to form alliances and battle against common foes, or go head-to-head in intense multiplayer modes.
     But the journey to victory won't be easy. Players must navigate treacherous terrain, avoid enemy fire, and strategically plan their attacks to outsmart their opponents. With challenging missions and epic boss battles, War Tank Machine offers a thrilling and immersive gaming experience that will keep players coming back for more.
     To succeed you must: 
- Upgrade your tank;
- Collect resources;
- Destroy the enemies;
- Win the war and, ultimately, 
- Have fun!
